{"tid":1305152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（保護自己 保護身邊人）自衛 制服罪犯係無罪","createTime":"2019-07-10T19:34:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T04:58:04.000Z","uid":98842,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b16bf5e80a4886481d0fcff73fb2e57dc2d1dc77","tid":1305152,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:34:18.000Z","msg":"根據香港法例 使用合理武力制止罪案, 係合法的 使用合理武力自衛, 係合法的 香港法律第221章《刑事訴訟程序條例》 101條： 在某些案件中循簡易程序拘捕罪犯 (2) <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">任何人可無需手令而逮捕任何他合理地懷疑犯了可逮捕的罪行的人。</span></span> 101A條： 作出逮捕時武力的使用等 (1) 任何人於防止罪案時或於進行或協助合法逮捕罪犯或疑犯或非法地不在羈留中的人時，可使用 就當時環境而言屬於合理的武力。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n保護好身邊人"},{"pid":"49ce44465d2cef0607ff9c3ce43b9f2610ec5941","tid":1305152,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:36:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20a057db4c55c2b4c38db82b2fdc0bdcf1254c8c","tid":1305152,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:38:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3c47b35ec9cea8dbf9ff0dcf89f626bdfce1052","tid":1305152,"uid":16624,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:39:24.000Z","msg":"法例會唔會保障你啊？醒啦仲法例"},{"pid":"4a4522809e0406869a4ce4544e0c57109ffcd37e","tid":1305152,"uid":98842,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b3c47b35ec9cea8dbf9ff0dcf89f626bdfce1052","tid":1305152,"uid":16624,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:39:24.000Z","msg":"法例會唔會保障你啊？醒啦仲法例"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:41:39.000Z","msg":"無可能入到你罪<br />\n<br />\n你由得身邊人比打<br />\n<br />\n係怕事"},{"pid":"59a36bf6394b8d89931a33474bbac99fdccd175c","tid":1305152,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b3c47b35ec9cea8dbf9ff0dcf89f626bdfce1052","tid":1305152,"uid":16624,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:39:24.000Z","msg":"法例會唔會保障你啊？醒啦仲法例"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:42:16.000Z","msg":"警察唔會保障你<br />\n但係法律仲有可能，如果遇到正常嘅